# Windows Server Installation

## Step 1: Create Virtual Machine
- Name: WindowsServer-Lab
- Type: Microsoft Windows
- Version: Windows 2019 (64-bit)
- Memory: 2048 MB
- CPU: 1 core

## Step 2: Attach ISO
- Attached Windows Server ISO to optical drive
- Booted VM

## Step 3: Installation Options
- Edition: Windows Server Standard (Desktop Experience)
- Installation type: Custom
- Disk: 50 GB unallocated space

## Step 4: Administrator Setup
- Set Administrator password to WinServer1
- Logged in successfully

## Result
Windows Server installed and accessible via console.

